title: Skateboarder Candy Jacobs talks Tony Hawk deal, Tokyo 2020, and more
description: Skateboarder Candy Jacobs is one of the most exciting street skaters on the contest scene. She's set to represent the Netherlands at Tokyo 2020. Find out how a DM from skating legend Tony Hawk changed her life and more.
